768
00:42:25,350 --> 00:42:26,270
Tak ada.

769
00:42:27,560 --> 00:42:28,430
Semangat!

770
00:42:31,190 --> 00:42:32,030
Kau sudah selesai bicara?

771
00:42:35,000 --> 00:42:35,680
Ada yang gerak.

772
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:37,880
Sudah bisa angkat pancingan, cepat.

773
00:42:38,520 --> 00:42:39,390
Tak bisa.

774
00:42:39,390 --> 00:42:40,760
Bukankah kau ingin belajar?

775
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:41,680
Tak mau bangun.

776
00:42:43,960 --> 00:42:45,800
Bao paling suka makan ikan.

777
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:46,880
Jika dia tahu ikan ini

778
00:42:46,880 --> 00:42:48,470
dipancing oleh Mamanya,

779
00:42:48,470 --> 00:42:49,640
dia pasti akan senang sekali.

780
00:42:52,070 --> 00:42:52,760
Cepat.

781
00:43:11,720 --> 00:43:12,880
Ikannya sudah terpancing.
